{"tid":2220610,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"少時最應該走一定係佢","createTime":"2020-09-27T19:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T19:16:45.000Z","uid":320858,"like":103,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6580673cae4d08894d779a63bbd771ecacc9efb4","tid":2220610,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T19:28:47.000Z","msg":"泰妍 大賞主唱 實力第一 個人出道I作詞 作為隊長表現功不可沒<br />\n<br />\nJessica 混血Barbie 唱跳全隊第二 音質獨特 kpop唯一冰山公主 時尚王<br />\n<br />\nTiffany 發言擔當 好勝心強 同sica同一醫院出世 海選第一<br />\n哈利波特認為最美少時成員<br />\n<br />\nSunny 可愛矮瓜擔當 必殺技wink搵鏡頭 皇族但是有實力<br />\n<br />\nYuri 運動戶外綜藝擔當 煮嘢食 拍戲<br />\n<br />\nHyoyeon Rapper 舞后 jazz hip pop popping locking balletbelly dance 都識 可惜沒太多舞台<br />\n<br />\n秀英 日文最流利 長腿擔當 填詞第一 最口臭<br />\n<br />\n允兒 C位 靠樣搵食十三年 CF queen 電影破九百萬人觀看 <br />\n唯一青龍90後入圍女主角<br />\n<br />\n徐賢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> TTS隊長 唱功第三  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sp67Kix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSp67Kix.jpg&h=a74aaaec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mYepiy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mYepiy.jpg&h=82702877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dv8xVqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDv8xVqe.png&h=f73a1b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/riLDQYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FriLDQYz.jpg&h=31961499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 8個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8841a5245520b3b6f3eb5258a83afce5437aa7e9","tid":2220610,"uid":320858,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T19:31:49.000Z","msg":"5個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AczX6xP.jpg\" data-thumb